<H3> <TI>   China Metallurgical Trade Fair Opens in Hong Kong </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1403045894 Beijing XINHUA in English 0408 GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1403045894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hong Kong, March 14 (XINHUA) -- A six-day China 
metallurgical export products trade fair opened here today in a 
bid to achieve overseas investment and cooperation. 
  On display are various metallurgical products manufactured 
by 
the China Metallurgical Import and Export Corporation and its 31 
subsidiaries. 
  It is learned that a large-scale metallurgical exhibition 
will open in Beijing on April 12. It would be the largest of 
its kind China would ever give. 

