...Among those present at the meeting were Chinese Vice Premier 
and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen; Vice Foreign Minister Tian 
Zengpei; U.S. Ambassador to China Stapleton Roy; Undersecretary 
of State Lynn Davis; and Undersecretary of Defense Frank Wiser. 
(adding additional material.) 

