Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By Debbie Kuo] </F>
  [Excerpt] Taipei, March 14 (CNA) -- Mikhail Gorbachev, 
former president of the now defunct Soviet Union, is scheduled 
to arrive in Taipei March 20 for a five-day visit at the 
invitation of the UNITED DAILY NEWS. 
